# WawaUI

A simple and lightweight Roblox UI library focused on being easy to use while looking clean.

## Features

- Clean interface
- Multiple tabs
- Toggle elements
- Dropdown menus
- Sliders
- Built-in themes
- Animated controls
- Easy to use

## Loading the Library

```lua
local Library = loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wawathegreat/WawaUi/main/WawaUI.lua"))()
```

## Creating a Window

```lua
local Window = Library.CreateWindow("My Script")
```

## Themes

```lua
Window:SetTheme("Dark")      -- Optional
Window:SetTheme("White")     -- Optional
Window:SetTheme("Midnight")  -- Optional
```

Available themes:

- Dark
- White
- Midnight

Changing the theme is optional.

## Creating Tabs

With an icon:

```lua
local Main = Window:AddTab(6031068426)
```

Without an icon:

```lua
local Main = Window:AddTab()
```

You can create as many tabs as you want.

## Toggle

```lua
Main:AddToggle(
    "ESP",
    "Toggle player ESP.", -- Optional description
    false, -- Default value
    function(Value)
        print(Value)
    end
)
```

## Dropdown

```lua
Main:AddDropdown(
    "Theme",
    {
        "Dark",
        "White",
        "Midnight"
    },
    function(Option)
        print(Option)
    end
)
```

## Slider

```lua
Main:AddSlider(
    "WalkSpeed",
    16, -- Minimum
    100, -- Maximum
    16, -- Default value
    function(Value)
        print(Value)
    end
)
```

## API

### Create Window

```lua
Library.CreateWindow(Title)
```

### Set Theme

```lua
Window:SetTheme(Theme)
```

### Create Tab

```lua
Window:AddTab(IconId)
```

### Toggle

```lua
Tab:AddToggle(Title, Description, DefaultValue, Callback)
```

### Dropdown

```lua
Tab:AddDropdown(Title, Options, Callback)
```

### Slider

```lua
Tab:AddSlider(Title, Minimum, Maximum, DefaultValue, Callback)
```

## Themes

| Available | Theme |
|:---------:|:------|
| ✅ | Dark |
| ✅ | White |
| ✅ | Midnight |

## Example

An `Example.lua` file is included in the repository demonstrating every feature currently available in WawaUI.